"     </tbody>",
"    </table>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     Type I: monoclonal immunoglobulin (Ig); Type II: mixed monoclonal Ig and polyclonal Ig; Type III: mixed polyclonal Ig. CLD: chronic liver disease; CTD: connective tissue disorder; LPD: lymphoproliferative or plasmaproliferative disorder; Essential: cases of symptomatic cryoglobulinemia that are not associated with a clear-cut CLD, CTD, LPD, or infection; Secondary: cases that are associated with a clear-cut CLD, CTD, LPD, or infection. + and &gt; indicate relative increasing frequency of occurence.",
